  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.6.6">
<l>uṉṉaic cintai ceytu ceytuṉ ṉeṭumā moḻiyicai pāṭiyāṭiyeṉ</l>
<l>muṉṉaitī viṉaikaḷ muḻuvē rarintaṉaṉyā</l>
<l>ṉuṉṉai cintaiyiṉā likaḻnta viraṇiya ṉakaṉmārvaṅ kīṇṭa veṉ</l>
<l>muṉṉaik kōḷariyē muṭiyāta teṉṉeṉakkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Constantly having thoughts [of you], singing you with long great word music, dancing</l>
<l>I have cut off the whole root of my former fiery karma/evil deeds.</l>
<l>O my former murderous lion who split the wide chest of Hiraṇya who slighted</l>
<l>you in thoughts, what would be impossible to me?</l>
    </lg>
    </div>
